<h1 Align="center"><font color="black" size="30"><b><u>Game Concept</b></u></font></h1>
<p Align="center"><font size="20">
I am going to create 2D video game on unity software that is going to be very enjoyable for everyone. The game
name is "Angry Bird".This game revolves around the birds.In this game we have few birds ,buildings structure,blocks etc.We 
have to hit the blocks,structure to collapse them and It depend on us how we throw the bird, with speed
or low, with different shapes and angles. The target of these birds is to distroy the blocks, building in order
 and complete there goal or mission. </font></p>
<h1 Align="center"><font color="black" size="30"><b><u>Genre</b></u></font></h1>
<p Align="center"><font size="20">
  This game is action based in this game angry birds are saving their eggs from their enemies. It is the fun gameplay. It is 2d game.WE have a animated movies on this game.
This game is soo enjoyable.</font></p>
<h1 Align="center"><font color="black" size="30"><b><u>Project Scope</b></u></font></h1>
<p Align="center"><font size="20">
The Scope of the project is Android game and funplay game. It have stages in this way player cann't get bored.There are also difficulty levels like hurdles,easy etc.
Player can select according  to it. Player have some number of birds then they have to hit the buildings etc in order to broke them. This type of game has no age restrictions.
</font>
</p>
<h1 Align="center"><font color="black" size="30"><b><u>Target Audience</b></u></font></h1>
<p Align="center"><font size="20">
Target Audience is general public So that everyone can play this game and there is no age restriction for these games.
